      <title>加拿大足球教练就奥运会无人机丑闻向球队道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/canadian-soccer-drone-scandal-prompts-government-to-dock-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大女子足球队在奥运会期间卷入无人机监视事件后，教练贝弗利·普里斯特曼公开道歉并承诺“承担责任”，此举引发国际足联的制裁和加拿大政府的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/canadian-soccer-drone-scandal-prompts-government-to-dock-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:00:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
